title: Game Plan, The [2007].AVI
description:
*** Plot Synopsis by Jason Buchanan 
Gridiron Gang star The Rock picks up the pigskin once again for this sports-themed family comedy concerning a football superstar who abandons the gridiron to answer the call of fatherhood after learning that he has a daughter he never knew. Kyra Sedgwick stars as the professional athlete&#039;s ruthless agent who would rather see her client scoring touchdowns than cementing familial bonds, and Nichole Millard teams with Kathryn Price to pen the screenplay.
